{"tid":1776782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"當年冇我推Momoland 連登會唔會有咁多人識?","createTime":"2019-12-09T18:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T08:22:25.000Z","uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2519cd27d54a47925ee658956eb79d845a6c15fa","tid":1776782,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDa2Ksw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDa2Ksw.jpg&h=c591cd0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZiDhNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZiDhNx.jpg&h=736784cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9007fd5bae82623602b4c452a4d7f2825f7dd060","tid":1776782,"uid":213163,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T18:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CJS6J8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CJS6J8.jpg&h=459c9125&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要聽晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n【國際人權日．正日集會】<br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQeOE4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQeOE4e.jpg&h=b94c0a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過20個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"0e0998c96704e56979a34a49714a312642f66743","tid":1776782,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"